{"tid":892793,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【收過首飾】王子生日點慶祝？鄧麗欣：太甜蜜會畀人笑甜到患糖尿","createTime":"2018-11-07T06:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T06:03:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"46e5b3f8cbbe04a1b7afe57939e47b694911836c","tid":892793,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:58:51.000Z","msg":"鄧麗欣(Stephy)今日到尖沙咀嘴出席手錶品牌活動，Stephy話自己向來好少收藏手錶：「不過依家都開始有興趣會望吓，以前一路無研究，原來有啲錶仲有升值潛力，唔似女仕啲首飾，通常我哋都會有好多唔同類型首飾。」<br />\nStephy透露男友都送過首飾畀佢，但講到錶就未試過：「男仔通常偏好大隻啲，我就鍾意啲細隻，而且每個人要求都唔同，都暫時未試過送錶。」嚟緊聖誕Stephy話已經開始煩惱送咩禮物：「近年尾又聖誕，又情人節，再遲啲就到佢生日，真係好難諗因為要每樣都唔同。」<br />\n剛過去嘅生日Stephy獲男友送上驚喜Party，早前兩個又曾經以情侶裝示人，Stephy話情侶裝係因宣傳需要，但強調：「自己都可以好浪漫，等我諗下點搞先。」又稱要好好考慮，否則表現得太甜蜜，會畀人笑甜到患糖尿。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541572935_df5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541572935_df5d.jpg&h=3c55cb77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541572936_a9e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541572936_a9e1.jpg&h=d7436aea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd2a69e600dad962e9ad29b26f737947fecca0d5","tid":892793,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T19:49:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24d4f668d15fd47a97026a787a6bcdb390f61a5b","tid":892793,"uid":29702,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T19:50:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82bdc60f5031a35113fb2bf836b233c2aa3bcf4a","tid":892793,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T19:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aec842b3d9e1e4a61ed8ff31d3cf258fafad43d","tid":892793,"uid":169468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T01:0